  "text": "For analysing the effect, smoothing and selecting an appropriate FWHM in a given ROI, the selected value of FWHM was the lowest leading to a significant cluster. This choice is justified by the concern of obtaining less extensive clusters, so better localized, and prevents regions that are functionally different from merging together [CITATION_1] .",
